BstNote.name: BstNote
BstNote.txtfile: The oral retelling of spoke words is kept here, almost as a manuscript: I am not long for this world. I have committed the ultimate sin, yet have no recollection of it. I am both here, and unhere. Come. Meet me in the tunnels beneath the tundra. There's a passageway to what remains of my timeline.
